  clientName: dadasdsa
  jobDescription: '"The old wooden bridge washed away in the storm. We need a quick
    replacement so the supply cart can cross the creek. Keep it simple, and remember:
    triangles make the strongest supports!"'
  budget: 51555
  liveLoadWeight: 411
  goldReward: 500
  expReward: 1000
  offerDialogue:
    name: 12421
    sentences:
    - Hey there! Ready for your first real job?
    - The storm washed out the crossing over Muddy Creek. We need to get a supply
      cart to the other side
    - You have a budget of $1500. Head over to the Drafting Table when you are ready
      to build.
  reminderDialogue:
    name: 412421
    sentences:
    - What are you waiting for? The creek isn't going to bridge itself!
    - Tap the Drafting Table to get started. Build across the gap and run the simulation.
  finishedContractDialogue:
    name: 421421
    sentences: []
